    <b><font size=+1>Week 6.&nbsp; Contagion?</font></b></center><br>
<img src="yerspestisc.jpg" width="600" height="24"></td>
</tr></table></center>

<p><table width="600" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0">
  <tr>
    <td>Supplementary readings for <b>Week 6</b>'s lectures include excerpts
from:
<ul><li>
