Fracastoro</a> (1478-1553);</li></ul>

<ul><li>
<i>Astronomia Magna</i> (1537) by <a href="week6h.html">Paracelsus</a> (1493-1541);</li></ul>

<ul><li>
<i>On Scarlet Fever</i> (1676) by <a href="week6b.html">Thomas
Sydenham</a> (1624-1689);</li></ul>

<ul><li>
<i>On the Measles</i> (1692) by <a href="week6c.html">Thomas
Sydenham</a>;</li></ul>

<ul><li>
<i>On Hooping Cough</i> (1752) by <a href="week6d.html">Nicholas
Ros&eacute;n von Rosenstein</a> (1706-1773);</li></ul>

<ul>
  <li>excerpts from
the <i>Diary</i> of Samuel Pepys (1633-1703):</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>
<a href="week6e.html">1664</a>;</li>

